# Deploy ifthink to Vercel

After making user-facing or site code changes in this repo (especially `index.html`):

1. Commit the relevant files (only when the change set is ready to ship, or when the user expects it live).
2. `git push origin HEAD` to GitHub (`ByeongJaeGo/ifthink`).
3. Ensure production is updated: GitHub integration usually redeploys, but if the live site may lag, run `npx vercel deploy --prod --yes`.
4. Tell the user the live URL: https://ifthink.vercel.app

Do not leave production on an old build after finishing a feature the user expects to see on the website.
